This short makeup video depicts how any eye needs to be enhanced keeping the eye shape in mind ... 
Blend and define until it satisfies you . Keep on blending until its smooth. 
keep your foundations minimal , let not your base rain in your face , as its a canvas .. Know when to stop ..

Show some love and feel free to drop in all your questions for this makeup tutorial 🙏

latestIgtvVideos.title: Short Lip tutorial
latestIgtvVideos.caption: While you do your makeup lips play an important part on your face . Do make sure you take care of making them up as much as you take care of your eyes. A lip liner is always important to use since it works as a framework to fit in the right shades , make your lips look contoured and also pouty at the same time . Cut through the sharp edges with a warm shade but simultaneously keeping in mind only the original lip color should pop out.  like mine was Coral by Dose of colors . That was the actual shade i wanted to elaborate.
